Rating: 3
A delicious recipe with wonderful flavours, but I made a couple of modifications that I felt enhanced the flavours. First, I sauteed the shallots, chile and lime zest together in a little oil for 5 minutes, added the lime juice and heated for another 2, then prepared the butter; this sweetened the shallots and blended the flavours much better than when the ingredients were raw. Secondly, I chose not to sautee the tilapia in oil; rather, I sauteed it in 2/3 the butter and saved the rest for the side. A much more flavourful result!

